            <p>An objective of this project is to conduct pre-background screening of employees before conducting interview. Utilizing background checks in hiring procedures can protect the company from future litigation charges related to hiring negligence, safeguard the companies’ assets and public relations, and make current employees feel safe and secure in their work environments. For these reasons, in combination with the fact that in today’s fast paced and globalized world it can be difficult to verify the details of a CV, background checks are an important part of many companies’ hiring procedures.</p>
            <p>This project act as a centralized system for employers and employees. Once a new company gets registered, that company details should be uploaded in this website.
Company should upload details of all employees such as Name, Contact details, Family details, Education details, Proof through which we can uniquely identify that employee throughout country(Voter ID no./ Adhaar card no.), work experience, Salary details, employee performance, department and domain in which employee is working, employee status i.e., still working or left and generating Unique Employ Number through which employee can be uniquely identified. If employee is applying for a next job, in his resume, he should specify 
Unique Employ Number along with his experience details or else he will be treated as a fresher.</p>
            <p >Companies going to receive resumes from the candidates as response for their job openings requirement. Before conducting interview, Company will check background of an employee using his Unique Employ Number, If company is satisfied with the employee background than company will schedule and intimate employee for interview. 

If there is any fraud in the resume of an employee then the company can remark on the employee profile.</p>
